thread.title: Doc
thread.title_full: The Logo Company reviewed by Doc

author: Doc
title: Doc
text: I went to The Logo Company with just the name of my new business and a very fuzzy concept. They were able to take my vague ideas and turn them into something that I am immensely proud of - and came up with the winning design on the first try. I have used them in the past for other logo designs and have been more than pleased, so I wasn't surprised that they would turn out high quality work on the first try! Recommended with no hesitation.
